A BILL
for
1 AN ACT relating to state lands; amending the duties of the
2 state forester; creating the wildfire management task
3 force; specifying members, duties and duration of the task
4 force; requiring reports; providing appropriations;
5 providing for the transfer of funds; authorizing borrowing;
6 repealing prior borrowing authorizations; and providing for
7 an effective date.
8
9 Be It Enacted by the Legislature of the State of Wyoming:
10
11 Section 1. W.S. 36-2-108(a), (b)(viii) and by
12 creating new paragraphs (ix) through (xi) is amended to
13 read:
14
1 SF0152

