17 (g) There is appropriated twenty-five thousand
18 dollars ($25,000.00) from the general fund to the office of
19 the governor for purposes of providing mileage and per diem
20 to the nonlegislative members of the task force. This
21 appropriation shall be for the period beginning with the
22 effective date of this act and ending June 30, 2027. This
23 appropriation shall not be transferred or expended for any
