5 Section 3.
6
7 (a) There is appropriated from the general fund for
8 the purpose of restoring funds expended by the state of
9 Wyoming to suppress wildfires that occurred in calendar
10 year 2024 the following amounts for the following programs
11 or purposes:
12
13 (i) One million dollars ($1,000,000.00) for the
14 special contingency division of the office of the governor,
15 unit 0601;
16
17 (ii) One million two hundred sixty-three
18 thousand nine hundred sixty-six dollars ($1,263,966.00) for
19 the disaster contingency unit within the homeland security
20 division of the office of the governor, unit 1106;
21
9 SF0152

